  <brief_title>Additive Effects of QVAR to (Seretide) on Surrogate Markers of Airway Inflammation in Refractory Asthma</brief_title>
  <acronym>PAW01</acronym>
  <official_title>A Proof of Concept Study to Evaluate the Additive Effects of HFA-BDP (Qvar) to Fluticasone/Salmeterol (Seretide) on Surrogate Markers of Small and Large Airway Inflammation in Refractory Asthma</official_title>
